title: Female vocal Pink Floyd covers FLAC EAC
description:
This is a great CD of female vocal covers of well known, and some not so well known Pink Floyd tracks. If you think that female vocals have no place in any Floyd song, then you only have to think back to 'The Great Gig In the Sky' The artists here are pretty obscure, but excellent. 

The recording/production is also very good with this album managing to sound killer on some very expensive audio systems I have played it through. 

The renditions here are good enough to stand on their own, especially the version of Wish You Were Here
